@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_meeqiw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.30 / v1 + 0.05)) / (wp.cos(v1 + 0.75) + wp.exp(v2 + 0.89)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.83)))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.73)
    v0 = (v0 * wp.cos(0.87))
    v0 = 0.71
    v2 = wp.sin((v2 * (v1 + 0.09 + v1 + 0.51)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.91)))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
